/**
 * The template for displaying all single solutions
 *
 * ACF-powered dynamic solution landing pages with WorldQuant particle system.
 * Replaces hardcoded content with dynamic ACF fields.
 *
 * @package AITSC_Pro_Theme
 * @since 3.1.0
